s" title="list of artifact types in archives" class="sf-depth-2">Artifacts</a></li><li id="menu-704-1" class="middle even sf-item-2 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/artwork" title="some sources of CLGA artwork" class="sf-depth-2">Artwork</a></li><li id="menu-1049-1" class="middle odd sf-item-3 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/audio-sound-recordings" class="sf-depth-2">Audio / sound recordings</a></li><li id="menu-1115-1" class="middle even sf-item-4 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/books-intro" class="sf-depth-2">Books</a></li><li id="menu-1110-1" class="middle odd sf-item-5 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/moving-images" class="sf-depth-2">Moving images</a></li><li id="menu-700-1" class="middle even sf-item-6 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/npc/home" title="view biographies, art descriptions" class="sf-depth-2">National Portrait Collection</a></li><li id="menu-2219-1" class="middle odd sf-item-7 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/newspapers/a-c" title="" class="sf-depth-2">Newspapers</a></li><li id="menu-1121-1" class="middle even sf-item-8 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/periodicals-lgbt" class="sf-depth-2">Periodicals</a></li><li id="menu-1111-1" class="middle odd sf-item-9 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/photographs" title="Our visual heritage in news shots, snaps, and fine works" class="sf-depth-2">Photographs</a></li><li id="menu-1112-1" class="middle even sf-item-10 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/posters" title="Preserving history right off the wall" class="sf-depth-2">Posters</a></li><li id="menu-1114-1" class="last odd sf-item-11 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/vertical-files" title="Material compiled on people, groups, and events" class="sf-depth-2">Vertical files</a></li></ul></li><li id="menu-1205-1" class="middle even sf-item-4 sf-depth-1 sf-total-children-5 sf-parent-children-0 sf-single-children-5 menuparent"><a href="/exhibitions/current" title="" class="sf-depth-1 menuparent">Exhibitions</a><ul><li id="men