<div id="block-views-spotlight-block-1" class="block block-views even region-count-2 clearfix">

    
  <div class="content">
    <div class="view view-spotlight view-id-spotlight view-display-id-block_1 view-dom-id-182d9f51c906e4ee07fc8d78153c19ff">
        
  
  
      <div class="view-content">
      
<div class="skin-default">
  
  <div id="views_slideshow_cycle_main_spotlight-block_1" class="views_slideshow_cycle_main views_slideshow_main"><div id="views_slideshow_cycle_teaser_section_spotlight-block_1" class="views-slideshow-cycle-main-frame views_slideshow_cycle_teaser_section">
  <div id="views_slideshow_cycle_div_spotlight-block_1_0" class="views-slideshow-cycle-main-frame-row views_slideshow_cycle_slide views_slideshow_slide views-row-1 views-row-odd">
  <div class="views-slideshow-cycle-main-frame-row-item views-row views-row-0 views-row-first views-row-odd">
    
  <div class="views-field views-field-field-spotlight-image">        <div class="field-content"><a href="http://clga.ca/we-could-be-heroes-just-one-day"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="http://www.clga.ca/sites/default/files/styles/spotlight/public/Untitled%20design%281%29.jpg?itok=XJCchf3B" width="215" height="225" alt="" /></a></div>  </div>  
  <div class="views-field views-field-title">        <span class="field-content"><a href="http://clga.ca/we-could-be-heroes-just-one-day">We Could Be Heroes (Just For One Day)</a></span>  </div>  
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>Running from March 24 to May 22, 2016 in “We Could be Heroes (Just for One Day),” Toronto photographer Tania Anderson turns this traditional search for heroes on its head. Through a series of fourteen portraits, she highlights diverse Toronto-based artists and activists who are rarely celebrated for their contributions to queer communities.</p>
</div>  </div></div>
</div>
<div id="views_slideshow_cycle_div_spotlight-block_1_1" class="views-slideshow-cycle-main-frame-row views_slideshow_cycle_slide views_slideshow_slide views-row-2 views_slideshow_cycle_hidden views-row-even">
  <div class="views-slideshow-cycle-main-frame-row-item views-row views-row-0 views-row-first views-row-odd">
    
  <div class="views-field views-field-field-spotlight-image">        <div class="field-content"><a href="/npc"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="http://www.clga.ca/sites/default/files/styles/spotlight/public/NPCmontage280x270.jpeg?itok=EvJDQ8P-" width="233" height="225" alt="Visit the National Portrait Collection" /></a></div>  </div>  
